    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Geth prioritizes local transactions. Local == submitted via the RPC or received from the network and recipient being in the `--txpool.locals` CLI flag (though you'll probable never get a 0 wei gas price tx propagated across the network). If you submit a tx to our miner directly with 0 gas price, it will pick it up before anything else.",
