    "created_at": "2021-01-06T08:32:54Z",
    "updated_at": "2021-01-06T08:32:54Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@TennisBowling this is not supported by geth. If you want to do that, you need to rewrite the transaction pool. We won't include such a change into geth as it leads to centralization. Being able to select specific transactions would enable the miner to censor other transactions, which should not be a feature in geth. If someone goes through the hoops of rewriting geth to do that, that's fine and nothing we can do about, but we will not add it as a feature.",
